 processes could explain the\nperiodicity seen in the New Horizons' data without the need for invoking\narbitrary solar wind conditions. The energetic particles generated by these\nprocesses are shown to map to the arc-like structures seen in the dusk side\nauroral features.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Jul 2016 20:37:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-07-11"}
