oved description of energetic LF from particle-\nand nucleus-induced reactions; showing a good agreement with a variety of\navailable experimental data. They have an improved predictive power compared to\nthe previous versions and can be used as reliable tools in simulating\napplications involving such types of reactions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Jul 2016 23:05:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-29"}
